            <header class="mvm">
              <h1>Periodic Certification of Fire Protection Systems Due May 31st</h1>
            </header>
            <p><span class="TextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun ContextualSpellingAndGrammarErrorV2Themed SCXW162563166 BCX8">In</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8"> an ong</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8">oing commitment to safety and compliance</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8">t</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8">he City of Philadelphia, Department of Licenses and Inspections </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8">remind</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8">s</span> <span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8">property owners</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8"> with fire </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8">protectio</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8">n</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8"> systems </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8">that </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8">some </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW162563166 BCX8">inspection certifications are due.</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW162563166 BCX8" data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}"> </span></p>
<p>Property owners should receive a <a href="https://www.phila.gov/documents/notice-of-fire-protection-inspection-certification/">notice of fire protection inspection certification </a>in the mail with more information.</p>
            <div class="post-meta mbm reveal-footer">
              <span class="date-published">Announced on: <time datetime="2024-03-11">March 11, 2024</time></span>
              <span class="departments"><a href="https://www.phila.gov/departments/department-of-licenses-and-inspections/">Department of Licenses and Inspections</a></span>
